                <note rend="inline" type="source">358.116 M 82/31: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Sweden</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Morris</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1921-04-09T18:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 9, 1921—6 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>21. Department’s No. 20, April 7, 6 p.m. Inform Swedish Government Mormon Church
                    invites any investigation Swedish Government may desire to make and will be glad
                    to pay expenses both to and from Utah of any investigator the Swedish Government
                    may desire to send.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
